reviews.text: Only went here for breakfast. It's no wonder it's pretty empty here compared to the other breakfast places next door. Eggs are tasty but overdone. Chicken had good flavour but needed gravy. Tea tastes like simple orange pekoe. I'll give it a try again for their actual fried chicken, just won't come here for breakfast again.

Extremely poor in term of efficiency. You probably have to wait for half hour before you reach the cashier. Better visit here if you have plenty of time.  

What a shame.
It's KFC, though a reasonably good one.
Service speed needs improvement to meet the standard of fast food.

result.name: 肯德基

reviews.text:
上日探訪上水匯肯德基家鄉雞食店 已然提及了 地方寬敞 座位舒適 可能因應食物素材 冷氣足夠。透心涼 且龐大玻璃幕牆  
配上舒適座位和美食 
 感覺良好。喜歡 欣賞她清雅淡然 眺望窗外景緻
吸引 全滿意  100分🔔讚賞。
好哇 尤如麥記的排隊選購包包等食物 早 午 晚三餐又如何 喜歡 可以了 年青人較隨意 吃的開懷 且上水匯肯德基座落地方潔淨舒適 。同時可以欣賞窗外建築物 遠眺山區美景緻 。太好了。
KFC一向是我的伙伴，因為很多套餐，平靚正！好好味！健康不？自己看啦！反正我都好健康。。

Only went here for breakfast. It's no wonder it's pretty empty here compared to the other breakfast places next door. Eggs are tasty but overdone. Chicken had good flavour but needed gravy. Tea tastes like simple orange pekoe. I'll give it a try again for their actual fried chicken, just won't come here for breakfast again.
正仆街，買六隻巴辣香雞翼俾五隻半，返到屋企先睇到
